{"tid":539881,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"出故照抄都有200正評？唐小鴨？？？","createTime":"2018-01-25T03:05:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-07T06:30:29.000Z","uid":72909,"like":207,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"23b0062eae5e94e71bb990b07e371bcd919097df","tid":539881,"uid":72909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T03:05:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">［睡前故事］訓前想聽故事既朋友們進來吧，也許你能找到一個使你安睡的故事<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/503224/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/503224/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n唐小鴨：<br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"color: blue;\">我睇過好多類型既小說同故事，所以可能會寫出黎個架構差唔多，請各位唔好見怪</span></blockquote><br />\n抄同參考差好遠下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 將個主角改左個名，重組下句字，就可以當係自己既故事？<br />\n<br />\n你可以話我唔抵得又好，小學雞又，我想表達下自己意見。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">係講故台眾多「原創」作品都係幾十正評既時候，請問唐小鴨憑咩可以過２００正評？</span></strong><br />\n當年Mr抄歌全城批鬥，因為大家尊重原創，話之你只係抄左一首，抄左就係抄。<br />\n見到<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">唐小鴨</span></strong>仲話想出書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，雖然已經叫不醒個班死忠，但希望唔好令到「抄襲」既人繼續荼毒大眾，令真正「原創」既人失去應有既尊重。<br />\n<br />\n ----------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n咁就無聊睇返其他巴絲既回覆啦，有巴打話：<br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"color: green;\">月老同晶片都睇過 九把刀寫既書</span></blockquote><br />\n唐小鴨回覆：<br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"color: blue;\">無錯呀巴打 <br />\n呢兩本書對我影響好大 印象深刻<br />\n呢兩篇既光環絕對屬於九把刀大大<br />\n我只係縮短左同埋加左啲個人元素落去</span></blockquote><br />\n個人元素係邊到？完全睇唔到。<br />\n<br />\n ----------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n有巴打回覆「第四夜下半夜 &ndash; 大腦晶片」：<br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"color: green;\">呢篇同九把刀篇紅線基本上一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></blockquote><br />\n結果得到６個負評<br />\n唐小鴨回覆：<br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"color: blue;\">呢兩篇可以話係向佢致敬<br />\n如果佢本人知道 要求我del 我都無咩所謂 <br />\n第時有機會出書 都未必會將呢兩篇納入<br />\nAnyway 多謝巴打意見</span></blockquote><br />\n分清楚致敬同抄未？<br />\n<br />\n ----------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n有絲打回覆：<br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"color: green;\">但希望巴打唔好再用殘體 好礙眼 近呢2篇都有幾隻字係咁</span></blockquote><br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"color: green;\">但感覺上用詞嘅style可以統一啲，一開始睇用詞以為係個背景係大陸，點知中間又夾雜咗啲港式粗口，再加原來係新界入camp先知係香港 <br />\n純粹小提點</span></blockquote><br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"color: green;\">好台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></blockquote><br />\n屌你老母，梗係啦。因為唐小鴨上大陸／台灣網，抄完然後重組句子，咁咪會有殘體字未改同埋唔道地囉。<br />\n<br />\n ----------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n我回覆「第一夜，下半夜──《松果》」：<br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"color: green;\">umm...好耐以前，我諗係睇高登飛揚既港男/港女FF妄誌已經提過兔子既愛情故事，跟著上網發現左呢個故事，個時應該係１６年。<br />\n希望你唔係抄。</span></blockquote><br />\n唐小鴨回覆：<br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"color: blue;\">最主要係其實<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">本身無諗過放上網</span></strong> 只係作黎私下比一個人睇 所以無諗咁多抄唔抄既野 佢睇得開心就得<br />\n所以會見到松果果個故事真係改動得好少 <br />\n尤其係小兔子系列係網上好盛行</span></blockquote><br />\n咁你而家又放上網？呢個係抄扮自己作既原因黎架咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n ----------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n有絲打回覆：<br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"color: green;\"><br />\n我幾年前已經睇過《三千年》呢個故事。你唔會同我講幾年前睇到個篇你就係原作者，又或者話你好鍾意呢個故事，所以想借鑑、加啲個人元素落去掛？咁請問你同搬字過紙、抄襲有乜分別？<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.xn--lhr56reoi3vbc24cwmu.tw/index.php/10-2013-12-28-03-04-24\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.xn--lhr56reoi3vbc24cwmu.tw%2Findex.php%2F10-2013-12-28-03-04-24&d=lYIdUSeY49PtrXZ8XFOxu%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=6abe0695\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.xn--lhr56reoi3vbc24cwmu.tw/index.php/10-2013-12-28-03-04-24</a><br />\n<br />\n其實前面已經有巴打提過係九把刀既書、舊登見過呢啲故事，但你仲可以一、兩句就敷衍了事，第時仲話要合輯成小說。大佬，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">你每隔幾篇就唔同文風，唔係指古風同現代既分別，係你現代都可以上一篇台腔、下一篇充滿大陸俗語。</span></strong>文筆更加唔洗講，《三千年》個篇一睇就知冇可能係你慣有既文筆水平，亦冇可能係幾星期內進步既程度。真心唔知你仲有幾多篇係打住「<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">好鍾意再加插個人元素」既幌子</span></strong>，實質係抄襲既短文。唔係個個都睇唔出架，樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n ----------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n唔再多講，各巴絲自己心水清，會自己判斷，如果要繼續支持佢我都阻止唔到。<br />\n其他講故台巴絲請加油，雖然可能暫時冇咩人睇到你地既努力，但好既野終會有人欣賞既。<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"7956f98611c72d6b17f7519e521eacf00eb65bfa","tid":539881,"uid":65743,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T03:05:44.000Z","msg":"右"},{"pid":"9a96db658484f283b02c004fd747c6fc3551f009","tid":539881,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T03:07:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dffaf34e84b75483dd2e9d402ba3f4d86c169ba","tid":539881,"uid":72909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T03:10:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57130a34104aa6233a1b6373f8573124e051fb09","tid":539881,"uid":72909,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T03:10:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de14d35873167595d0e56f66898b64761cbb6225","tid":539881,"uid":72909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T03:15:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"954f6e2435036fdbfb6e3bef32e7efe1d4c552f3","tid":539881,"uid":160175,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T03:16:03.000Z","msg":"屌終於有人講，睇到好撚嬲，次次都用致敬、參考呢啲理由黎推脫，唔會放入書到出版就大曬咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔明點撚解仲有人一直支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e5faf58ae4da74448d26dbbde011713042fa485","tid":539881,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T03:16:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e9682534e6d87efacda666c3341d01216e6bc07","tid":539881,"uid":72909,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T03:18:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5ad6563fe98fe3523a80d538eb460625cd68305","tid":539881,"uid":72909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T03:21:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f85d6fcb945e4e4f619c53c04bf42a9bb105b01","tid":539881,"uid":72909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T03:53:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb263d9a8d6f7e1d913ba9e060edfed0d5e338f2","tid":539881,"uid":72909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T04:00:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b2d37ac5b9b0b545c8cc12734e667648dd322ca","tid":539881,"uid":72909,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T04:01:20.000Z","msg":"如果咁多位巴絲唔講，你實繼續話係你「原創」架啦"},{"pid":"96913372b62557199fb77142b46b5c417ba3ebe6","tid":539881,"uid":72909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T04:15:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dae95b9f9ceb0c93befa76c09b1fc267e10ad32","tid":539881,"uid":72909,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T04:28:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"142bedc0db762b9b8b370978149f23fb1c09329c","tid":539881,"uid":103470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T05:11:50.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"c5d6b2046cb2c52aa19d432f376cdafe51c3189d","tid":539881,"uid":3454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T05:21:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9a4e12b4a684d4cacf9518897e50563f540fd66","tid":539881,"uid":19981,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T05:52:15.000Z","msg":"仲講到自己會出書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，瞓醒未啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e4e056903e2813f4f724f3967023a5d8c612922","tid":539881,"uid":72909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T06:08:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"770049d68c6d99fcf5e2585b3306614a1a4f69da","tid":539881,"uid":10453,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T06:08:34.000Z","msg":"網絡上其實都好多二創、致敬作品，大家都會落明出處，唔寫出處又點知你致敬邊個、二創邊個？除非你嘅作品只係參考某啲作品嘅概念，劇情、人設等等材料係完全唔同，否則連文句都抄埋或者只係改三幾個字眼嘅抄考最好都係落返出處，等人踢爆就會令其他人覺得你只係想側側膊咁盜用人哋作品，到時大家都無癮。<br />\n<br />\n如果非牟利抄考吓作品去改篇其實都算無傷大雅，唔少同人二創都幾好睇。"},{"pid":"47c14d68e20456c382a372ad0db647d47953829f","tid":539881,"uid":160175,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e9a4e12b4a684d4cacf9518897e50563f540fd66","tid":539881,"uid":19981,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T05:52:15.000Z","msg":"仲講到自己會出書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，瞓醒未啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T06:09:12.000Z","msg":"佢試下出，侵犯知識產權用作商業用途分分鐘可以告佢刑事。"},{"pid":"633a0461f9faaa9d6a35c928dc2bf96394be1e49","tid":539881,"uid":160175,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"770049d68c6d99fcf5e2585b3306614a1a4f69da","tid":539881,"uid":10453,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T06:08:34.000Z","msg":"網絡上其實都好多二創、致敬作品，大家都會落明出處，唔寫出處又點知你致敬邊個、二創邊個？除非你嘅作品只係參考某啲作品嘅概念，劇情、人設等等材料係完全唔同，否則連文句都抄埋或者只係改三幾個字眼嘅抄考最好都係落返出處，等人踢爆就會令其他人覺得你只係想側側膊咁盜用人哋作品，到時大家都無癮。<br />\n<br />\n如果非牟利抄考吓作品去改篇其實都算無傷大雅，唔少同人二創都幾好睇。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T06:11:02.000Z","msg":"佢俾人踢爆之後唔係話致敬就話參考，岩岩仲覆左我話因爲最近遇到人生挫折先乜乜乜，真係人無恥便無敵。"},{"pid":"adf2185c9112ec1698b3701d047691cfbab2290c","tid":539881,"uid":72909,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T06:18:49.000Z","msg":"藉口１：　唔夠時間<br />\nＫＯＬＯＲ之前都一月一歌，所以又可以抄？<br />\n藉口２：　讀者睇得開心<br />\nＭＲ既歌都好好聽，係咪代表佢冇抄先？<br />\n<br />\n咁撚多藉口，垃圾。"},{"pid":"f6473d19f2a1cbeb98d3c10635f8f5808f0daeb7","tid":539881,"uid":14910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T06:22:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aa804d0fc3dd38463d0ae598dfdd194849fefa86","tid":539881,"uid":72801,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T06:23:38.000Z","msg":"係咪打算恰連登仔唔睇書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n抄故就想出書  醒未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8548f78d0a973851d52ac1cd5f5f8216fc5fcc71","tid":539881,"uid":72909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T06:26:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"413382335c2be20993d777d87eea694886254a97","tid":539881,"uid":57580,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T06:29:46.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"8bfd01ad03904dc48e006678e9b11b50b164a1b2","tid":539881,"uid":72909,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T06:35:20.000Z","msg":"駁唔到，Ｄ fans淨係識負評？"},{"pid":"2ebf85f9f5f1dd2d6183e093083b90a96afb0d35","tid":539881,"uid":72909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T06:49:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a507e6642d599ca8186e22fd65f17dd46c08667b","tid":539881,"uid":19981,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T06:49:35.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，最憎啲人抄野扮自己作"},{"pid":"c8a011ef4cc39d7ba10ed202de5e48d5d207997b","tid":539881,"uid":72909,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T06:53:22.000Z","msg":"仲要係自己ＰＯＳＴ係咁講到自己好岩咁，你含撚啦。我好多時間，一定慢慢追擊你。"},{"pid":"aba6a6c01fbaaf1e79a8e46705e92fc35180de54","tid":539881,"uid":74598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T06:55:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6aad69b639047f8f44b60b9b449d2b804da1488f","tid":539881,"uid":4131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T06:56:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6ac4ba93237a83c0bf4e7795f90519d8d5d81bf9","tid":539881,"uid":82720,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T06:56:51.000Z","msg":"搵藉口能力仲高過創作能力"},{"pid":"4de647baf41d9fc11bed244db81e250251597d62","tid":539881,"uid":72909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T07:24:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e30dc7d48574fd27aa10db5a206065d14f2b32c2","tid":539881,"uid":48579,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T07:33:18.000Z","msg":"講故台就係咁 <br />\n低質往往先多人睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86189c05193fdfacd8465b56f2eaacae5a004fdc","tid":539881,"uid":7107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T07:34:37.000Z","msg":"抄九把X咁冇品味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a2af2c82fda3c467474deb5ab1c927b05d558b9","tid":539881,"uid":72909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T08:02:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"363e573374fe2c8af591ec597ac72700e47f00e5","tid":539881,"uid":72909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-0